    • onTabComplete

      public List<String> onTabComplete(org.bukkit.command.CommandSender sender, org.bukkit.command.Command command, String alias, String[] args)
      Provides tab completion options for this command. This method is called by Bukkit when a player attempts to tab-complete this command. The default implementation returns an empty list. Override this method to provide custom tab completion options.
      Specified by:
      onTabComplete in interface org.bukkit.command.TabCompleter
      Parameters:
      sender - The entity requesting tab completion
      command - The command being tab-completed
      alias - The alias being used for the command
      args - The arguments passed to the command so far
      Returns:
      A list of possible tab completions
